cu.explanation_en: Setting the S1U port to 0 will cause connection failure as port 0 is invalid and unreachable, leading to NGU interface setup rejection.

du.explanation_en: Changing the local network address to an unreachable subnet IP will cause routing failure and prevent F1 interface connection to the CU.
du.explanation_zh: 將本地網路地址更改為不可達的子網 IP 會導致路由失敗，並阻止與 CU 的 F1 介面連接。
